    "link": "https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/events\/an-inspiring-evening-with-david-suzuki-tara-cullis\/",
    "title": {
        "rendered": "An Inspiring Evening with David Suzuki &amp; Tara Cullis!"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<div style=\"height:31px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>David Suzuki and Tara Cullis are coming to the\u00a0Burlington Performing Arts Centre (BPAC)\u00a0on\u00a0March 8th,\u00a0and BurlingtonGreen is proud to be a partner for this special event.<br><br><em><a href=\"https:\/\/burlingtonpac.ca\/events\/what-you-wont-do-for-love\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">What You Won\u2019t Do For Love<\/a><\/em> is a special event that is expected to sell out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Join us for a powerful opportunity to gather, reflect, and feel inspired by voices that have shaped environmental action for decades.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SPECIAL OFFER: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/newsletter-signup\/\"> Sign up <\/a>to receive BurlingtonGreen&#8217;s popular e-newsletter, and you&#8217;ll receive a promo code for 25% off\u00a0your tickets. (while tickets remain available)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also purchase tickets <a href=\"https:\/\/burlingtonpac.ca\/events\/what-you-wont-do-for-love\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here<\/a>, while seats remain.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/burlingtonpac.ca\/events\/what-you-wont-do-for-love\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\" noreferrer noopener\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-30432\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026-18x10.jpg 18w, https:\/\/www.burlingtongreen.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/suzuki_content_2026.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-bg-button-default\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-light-color has-green-darkest-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/burlingtonpac.ca\/events\/what-you-wont-do-for-love\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">EVENT TICKETS<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><br><strong>What others are saying:<\/strong><br><br><em>\u201cA deeply personal, totally enchanting love story. David and Tara take us on a magical journey into the heart of commitment \u2013 to one another, to family, to community, to justice and to the planet. A testament to hope.\u201d<\/em><br><br>\u2013 Maude Barlow (Author and activist, founding member of the Council of Canadians, co-founder of the Blue Planet Project)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>\u201cWarm, wise and overflowing with generosity, this is a love story so epic it embraces all of creation. Yet another reminder of how blessed we are to be in the struggle with elders like David and Tara.\u201d<\/em><br><br>\u2013 Naomi Klein (author, journalist, social activist, and filmmaker) and Avi Lewis (filmmaker, climate activist, educator)<\/p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
        "rendered": "<p>David Suzuki and Tara Cullis are coming to the\u00a0Burlington Performing Arts Centre (BPAC)\u00a0on\u00a0March 8th,\u00a0and BurlingtonGreen is proud to be a partner for this special event. What You Won\u2019t Do For Love is a special event that is expected to sell out. Join us for a powerful opportunity to gather, reflect, and feel inspired by voices [&hellip;]<\/p>\n",
